prove:
    have f set
    know:
        $restrict_fn_in(f, fn(x R, y Q) R)

    f(1, 2) = f(1, 2)

prove:
    forall f restrictive(fn(x R, y Q) R):
        f(1, 2) = f(1, 2)

prove:
    abstract_prop p(x)

    know:
        forall f restrictive(fn(x R, y Q) R):
            $p(f)

    have f fn(x R, y Q) R
    $p(f)